comments: Irving (DAL) legally contests the driving shot attempt by Reaves (LAL) and any contact that occurs as he returns to the floor is marginal.
Irving (DAL) moves alongside of Reaves (LAL), who extends his left leg outwards to create any marginal contact that occurs.
James (LAL) tips the ball in when it is outside of the imaginary cylinder above the basket ring.
Doncic (DAL) briefly has a hand on the ball, but Prince (LAL) is able to pull it away and establish full control.  Any contact from Doncic is incidental.
Irving (DAL) legally contests James's (LAL) jump shot attempt.

Russell (LAL) and Hardaway Jr. (DAL) briefly engage and disengage on the perimeter.  Russell extends his left arm after the contact dissolves, but the contact with Doncic (DAL) does not affect his SQBR.
Holmes (DAL) is in the paint for longer than three seconds without imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Doncic (DAL) cleanly deflects the pass from James (LAL) away from Davis (LAL) and any contact that occurs is incidental.
Reaves (LAL) commits a take foul on Irving (DAL).
Reaves (LAL) commits a take foul on Irving (DAL).
Exum (DAL) legally contests James's (LAL) jump shot attempt.
